entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You completed your primary and secondary mission.
entries.journal_entry_description: Do your best to evacuate the survivors and complete your primary mission.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: [Captain Piett] You've done all you can there. Get out while you still can!
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Use the ladder to leave the facility.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Move out of the way to allow the survivors to make a run for it.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: [Captain Piett] Cover those survivors as they try to escape! Their experience is invaluable.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Do your best to protect the survivors while they run to safety.
entries.task05_comm_message_text: [Captain Piett] Great work. Now all you have to do is get out of there. See if HX-138 has the shuttle ready.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Speak to HX-138 to see if the shuttle has been repaired.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Speak to Captain Piett for a debriefing.
entries.task08_comm_message_text: We owe you our lives. I can't begin to tell you how much I appreciate all you have done.
